snippet.title: Okay Fine, I'll Play Turnabout Pairs... [FT] [1]
snippet.description:
[A Visual Novelty First-Time Agony]

The long-awaited sequel to Turnabout of Courage starts with an agonized scream (mine) and ends with a bit of an intriguing locked room in a setting that should be familiar to Ace Attorney fans? Okay, I'm suffering but I'm hanging around for now...
-----------------------------------------
Turnabout Pairs, by Bad Player [You know what you've done]
And Blackrune too? [You know what you've done]

Find it on AA Online here: http://aaonline.fr/player.php?trial_id=36717

It's the sequel to Turnabout of Courage, what more do you need to know? :)
